## Acknowledgments

This project builds upon several excellent open source libraries:

- **React** (MIT License) - A JavaScript library for building user interfaces
  Copyright (c) Facebook, Inc. and its affiliates.

- **marked** (MIT License) - A markdown parser and compiler
  Copyright (c) 2018+, MarkedJS contributors

- **DOMPurify** (Apache License 2.0 / Mozilla Public License 2.0) - DOM-only XSS sanitizer
  Copyright (c) 2015 Mario Heiderich

- **html2canvas** (MIT License) - Screenshots with JavaScript
  Copyright (c) 2012 Niklas von Hertzen

- **react-image-crop** (ISC License) - A responsive image cropping tool for React
  Copyright (c) 2014 Dominic Tobias

- **clsx** (MIT License) - A tiny utility for constructing className strings conditionally
  Copyright (c) Luke Edwards

We are grateful to the maintainers and contributors of these projects for their excellent work
that makes this WYSIWYG editor possible.

